author: Ryan Shirley
description:
With tourism back to normal, 2026 is going to be a year full of travel. Enjoy this travel guide featuring some of the best places to visit this year. From hiking the scenic mountains of Patagonia, to snorkeling in the tropical waters of Bora Bora, I hope you can visit some new destinations this year. Where do you want to travel most in 2026?
